---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import { WA_LINKS } from '../../lib/constants';
---

<Base
  title="Layanan SBU & SKK Konstruksi"
  description="Semua compliance kontraktor, satu pintu. 4 cluster, 17 layanan. Dari sertifikasi utama sampai tender document support."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy-900 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight text-white md:text-5xl">
          Semua compliance kontraktor, satu pintu.
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 md:text-xl">
          4 cluster. 17 layanan. Dari sertifikasi utama sampai tender document support — semua ditangani satu tim.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4 Cluster Cards -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-20">
    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">

      <!-- Sertifikasi Utama -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-navy-700/50 bg-navy-800 p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-white">Sertifikasi Utama</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">SBU, SKK, Serkom, KTA — semua kualifikasi K, M, B dengan audit awal dan garansi output.</p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>SBU Jasa Konstruksi (baru, perpanjangan, perubahan, tambah subklasifikasi)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>SBU Kelistrikan (baru, perpanjangan, perubahan, tambah subklasifikasi)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>SKK — semua jenjang (J5, J6, J7, J8, J9)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>Serkom (Sertifikat Kompetensi) untuk SBU Kelistrikan</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>KTA (Keanggotaan Asosiasi Profesi)</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/layanan/sertifikasi-utama" class="mt-6 inline-block text-gold-400 hover:underline">Lihat Detail →</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Pendukung Pemenuhan SBU -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-navy-700/50 bg-navy-800 p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-white">Pendukung Pemenuhan SBU</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">KAP, ISO, peralatan teknik, dan dokumen legal yang sering jadi stumbling block.</p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>Laporan Keuangan KAP (Kantor Akuntan Publik)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>ISO 37001 Akreditasi KAN</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>Persyaratan Peralatan Teknis</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>Dokumen Pengalaman / Kontrak Referensi</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/layanan/pendukung-sbu" class="mt-6 inline-block text-gold-400 hover:underline">Lihat Detail →</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Maintenance Compliance -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-navy-700/50 bg-navy-800 p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-white">Maintenance Compliance</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Compliance periodik — jangan sampai lewat deadline.</p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>LKPM (Laporan Kegiatan Penanaman Modal)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>Surveilans / Monitoring LSBU</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>SBU Monitoring & Perubahan Data</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>OSS Compliance Maintenance</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/layanan/maintenance-compliance" class="mt-6 inline-block text-gold-400 hover:underline">Lihat Detail →</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Tender & Compliance Tambahan -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-navy-700/50 bg-navy-800 p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-white">Tender & Compliance Tambahan</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Sering muncul sebagai syarat tender atau compliance proyek.</p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>SMK3 Kemenaker</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>ISO 9001 / 14001 / 45001</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>BPJS Ketenagakerjaan</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>KSWP / Kepatuhan Pajak</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>PKKPR, PBG / SLF</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>NIB / KBLI / Sinkronisasi OSS</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-gold-400">✓</span>
            <span>Bank Garansi & Tender Document Support</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/layanan/tender-dan-sbu" class="mt-6 inline-block text-gold-400 hover:underline">Lihat Detail →</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom CTA -->
  <section class="bg-navy-900 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-20 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-white md:text-4xl">Butuh konsultasi layanan yang tepat untuk proyek Anda?</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-gray-300">Tim kami akan bantu identifikasi layanan yang paling relevan — tanpa biaya, tanpa komitmen.</p>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a
          href={WA_LINKS.general}
          class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-gold-500 px-10 py-4 font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-navy-900 shadow-lg shadow-gold-500/20 transition hover:bg-gold-400"
        >
          Konsultasi Gratis via WhatsApp →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
